WEBVTT

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:12.350
[Music]

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:14.869
[Music]
Make us remember

00:00:14.879 --> 00:00:19.150
You fragments of yesterday still alive in us

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:23.670
Oh, the brutal ache of missing it all

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:27.630
The craving has left us weeping

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.269
Talk to us

00:00:30.279 --> 00:00:34.549
Why are these walls so dead and silent?

00:00:34.559 --> 00:00:38.950
Could they really turn cold and forget us?

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:42.990
But being a stranger in your own soul is so much crueler

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.470
>> Make us remember

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:49.709
You fragments of yesterday still alive in us

00:00:49.719 --> 00:00:54.229
Oh, the brutal ache of missing it all

00:00:54.239 --> 00:00:58.270
The craving has left us weeping

00:00:58.280 --> 00:01:00.869
Talk to us

00:01:00.879 --> 00:01:05.109
Why are these walls
so dead and silent?

00:01:05.119 --> 00:01:09.510
Could they really turn cold and forget us?

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:13.510
But being a stranger in your own soul is so much crueler

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:16.109
>> Take us back

00:01:16.119 --> 00:01:20.390
Let us taste those sweet years again

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:24.789
To remember a past that meant everything

00:01:24.799 --> 00:01:28.710
Our old streets and the people who breathed life into them

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:31.270
Tell us

00:01:31.280 --> 00:01:33.429
About the stories of our childhood

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:35.749
And those timid, early days

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:37.870
How they rushed through our lives

00:01:37.880 --> 00:01:40.030
>> Gather our shattered pieces

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:42.230
From this scattered mess we're living in

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:43.990
And hold us

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:46.550
And ask this grieving house

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:48.389
Did it feel the same warmth we once felt?

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:50.950
>> And ask us

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:55.310
How the ache suddenly flared up

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:59.270
When the sheikh called to prayer and led us

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:01.870
Tears poured out when you finally answered us

00:02:01.880 --> 00:02:06.389
Tell this exhausted heart

00:02:06.399 --> 00:02:10.630
Have our fathers really left us behind?

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:17.229
Every corner of these streets is crying out

00:02:17.239 --> 00:02:21.470
Make us remember

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:25.910
A home that was made of us, living right inside us

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:30.750
Where we lived for so many years

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:32.390
Safe, and at peace

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:36.710
[Applause]

